{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues/task-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Pročitao sam članak o pravilu Tona Sandhi.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<h2>Pravila Pinyin-a - Tonski sandhi</h2>\n<p>Nauči samo prvu laku reč na kineskom, <ruby>你好<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ hǎo</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>. Možda ste primetili da se izgovara kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ní hǎo</span>. Zašto?</p>\n<p>Sve <ruby>你<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> i <ruby>好<rp>(</rp><rt>hǎo</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> su napisani u trećem tonu (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">ˇ</span>). Ali kada to izgovoriš zajedno, kažeš dva treća tona. To je teško izgovoriti. Zato kineski ima pravilo koje se zove:</p>\n<p><strong>Pravilo kombinovanja tona</strong>: Ton 3 + Ton 3 → Ton 2 + Ton 3</p>\n<p>Kada se dve sloge trećeg tona pojave zajedno, prva sloga se menja u drugi ton (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">ˊ</span>) a druga sloga ostaje treći ton (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">ˇ</span>). Pišeš početne tone, ali ih izgovaraš drugačije.</p>\n<p>Ovde su više primera pravila Tona Sandhi u delovanju:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Neno</th>\n<th>Značenje</th>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Inasemwa</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">美好</span></td>\n<td>lijep/dobar</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">měi hǎo</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">méi hǎo</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">想法</span></td>\n<td>misao</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">xiǎng fǎ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">xiáng fǎ</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">很好</span></td>\n<td>vrlo lijepo/vrlo dobro</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">hěn hǎo</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">hén hǎo</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">手表</span></td>\n<td>sat</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shǒu biǎo</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">shóu biǎo</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">所以</span></td>\n<td>tako/ovako</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">suǒ yǐ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">suó yǐ</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">可以</span></td>\n<td>može</td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">kě yǐ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ké yǐ</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues/task-4"},"questions":[],"scene":null,"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 4","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/#zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues","dashedName":"task-4","certification":"a1-professional-chinese","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","chapter":"zh-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"zh-a1-module-greetings-and-basic-introductions","block":"zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues/task-5","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues/task-3","id":"68d938aa5911e058ecd6862c","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagu